    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1889960/extras/bb118cc3073d1a4f18383eb145eeed6f.avif?t=1687085361\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1889960/extras_big/bb118cc3073d1a4f18383eb145eeed6f.avif?t=1687085361 width=800 height=72 /></span><br><br><strong><u>这是怎么回事？</u></strong><br><br>在弗林王子和夏甲王子兄弟发动入侵后，奥达里亚王国陷入混乱。塞德里克的家人分散在王国各处，他的目标是拯救他的家人并夺回他们在哈芬登的家。<br><br><strong><u>基于动作的战斗</u></strong><br><br>使用游戏中实施的基于动作的战斗系统在战斗中完全控制塞德里克。无论您是攻击、使用盾牌还是使用物品，选择权都在您手中！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1889960/extras/8140837ff1d642f5a0207c9aa0066283.poster.avif?t=1687085361\" width=654 height=368 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1889960/extras/8140837ff1d642f5a0207c9aa0066283.webm?t=1687085361\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1889960/extras/8140837ff1d642f5a0207c9aa0066283.mp4?t=1687085361\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1889960/extras/8a8f137ab19520f58b9321f2ab7978cb.poster.avif?t=1687085361\" width=654 height=368 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1889960/extras/8a8f137ab19520f58b9321f2ab7978cb.webm?t=1687085361\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1889960/extras/8a8f137ab19520f58b9321f2ab7978cb.mp4?t=1687085361\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong><u>自定义配乐</u></strong><br><br>穿越小达里亚的各个地点，欣赏独特的声音，帮助您沉浸在世界中。<br><br><strong><u>还有更多的事情要做！</u></strong><br><br>奥达里亚的王国有各种各样的问题困扰着他们，以及入侵的终极威胁。帮助重建它们，解决谜题，阻止罪犯，甚至收集和升级你的盔甲，以协助你将面临的许多战斗。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1889960/extras/de161915126d00ee1df12cb8252962aa.poster.avif?t=1687085361\" width=654 height=368 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1889960/extras/de161915126d00ee1df12cb8252962aa.webm?t=1687085361\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1889960/extras/de161915126d00ee1df12cb8252962aa.mp4?t=1687085361\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>   - 欢乐时光<br>   - 游戏内支持键盘和控制器<br>   - 充满活力，色彩缤纷的2D风格世界<br>   - 引人入胜的故事<br>   - 大量额外的副业",
